            <thetext>There is a bug in Internet Explorer 11, which occurs when using flex-box layout.
The text-wrapping gets broken.

I have found a solution at Stack Overflow:

http://stackoverflow.com/questions/18937476/how-do-you-word-wrap-in-firefox-and-ie-10-while-using-display-moz-box-and-ms


We have to wrap the label by a &lt;p&gt; and assign a  
-ms-flex: 1;
box-flex: 1;</thetext>
